nodes.text: A clone trooper pilot flew with the Galactic Republic's Blue Squadron early in the Clone Wars, participating in the Battle of Muunilinst as a V-19 Torrent starfighter pilot under Jedi Commander Anakin Skywalker.

During the battle, the clone trooper pilot reported to Commander Skywalker that nearly all of the InterGalactic Banking Clan's gun platforms had been destroyed. However, his report was interrupted by the arrival of a Ginivex-class starfighter piloted by Asajj Ventress, who quickly killed the clone trooper and the rest of his squadron.
